First, let's get the equation in vertex form by completing the square:
\begin{align*}
x^2 - 5x - 4 &\le 10\\
x^2 - 5x &\le 14\\
\left(x-\dfrac{5}{2}\right)^2 &\le \left(\dfrac{2\sqrt{14}}{2}\right)^2\\
\left(x-\dfrac{5}{2}\right)^2 &\le 7
\end{align*}

